OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777014326
OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FSacked Foreign Office official refused
OL,7,Fto hand over key files relating to
OL,8,FPeter Mandelson's vetting process,
OL,9,Faccording to the Prime Minister's
OL,10,FCabinet Office chief.
OL,12,FAppearing before the Foreign Affairs
OL,13,FCommittee, Cat Little, the most senior
OL,14,Fcivil servant at the Cabinet Office,
OL,15,Fsaid she held "multiple discussions"
OL,16,Fwith Robbins, the former Foreign
OL,17,FOffice chief, over the release of the
OL,18,FMandelson files.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
