CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777014326
OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FRobbins appeared before the committee
OL,7,Fearlier this week, just days after the
OL,8,Fprime minister sacked him as Foreign
OL,9,FOffice chief for failing to inform him
OL,10,Fabout details of the vetting decision
OL,11,Fon Mandelson.
OL,13,FLittle disputed claims made by Robbins
OL,14,Fthat her department had suggested
OL,15,FMandelson may not have needed vetting
OL,16,Fdue to his status as a peer in the
OL,17,FHouse of Lords, stating it was the
OL,18,FForeign Office that had raised the
OL,19,Finitial conversation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
