PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777014326
OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,F"Because the presumption had been that
OL,7,Fgiven Peter Mandelson had been a
OL,8,Fmember of the House of Lords, the long-
OL,9,Fstanding convention that he didn't
OL,10,Frequire developed vetting was assumed,
OL,11,Fand they wanted to get proper policy
OL,12,Fadvice from experts on whether that
OL,13,Fwas the case," she said, referring to
OL,14,Fdocuments that showed such a
OL,15,Fdiscussion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
