OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FGiving evidence to MPs, she said that
OL,7,Fdue process was followed during the
OL,8,Fvetting process and that she had been
OL,9,Funcovering documents related to the
OL,10,Fpeer's appointment to the role being
OL,11,Freleased under the humble address
OL,12,Fprocess forced by MPs in February.
OL,14,F"So my view is that due process was
OL,15,Ffollowed, and if I might explain why I
OL,16,Fbelieve that it is because the process
OL,17,Fas I've outlined to the committee, is
OL,18,Fthat UKSV (UK Security Vetting) make a
OL,19,Frecommendation and the Foreign Office
OL,20,Fmake a decision as to whether to grant
OL,21,FDV (developed vetting).
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
