CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777014326
OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,F"That is the process, and that is the
OL,7,Fprocess that is agreed with the
OL,8,FForeign Office," Ms Little said.
OL,10,FLittle last week told the prime
OL,11,Fminister that Mandelson had been
OL,12,Fgranted high-level security clearance
OL,13,Fdespite vetting officials recommending
OL,14,Fagainst it.
