OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FShe had known since March 25 about
OL,7,Fsensitive information linked to
OL,8,FMandelson's vetting - but rather than
OL,9,Ftell the prime minister immediately,
OL,10,Fshe sought expert legal advice about
OL,11,Fhow to deal with such sensitive
OL,12,Finformation.
OL,14,FLittle said that when Robbins refused
OL,15,Fto share vetting information with her,
OL,16,Fshe took the "very unusual" decision
OL,17,Fto request it from security officials
OL,18,Fdirectly.
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
