OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777014326
OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,F"I did that because I go back to my
OL,7,Fresponsibilities to discharge the
OL,8,Fhumble address, which is a
OL,9,Fresponsibility that is unique to me,
OL,10,Fand I take very seriously.
OL,12,F"I felt that I needed to see some
OL,13,Frelevant documentation so that I could
OL,14,Fadvise the prime minister as to
OL,15,Fwhether we had fully complied and
OL,16,Fgathered the information that was
OL,17,Favailable and within scope."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@\O]
