OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FLabour backbenchers have openly voiced
OL,7,Fdoubts about Starmer's future since it
OL,8,Femerged last week the Foreign Office
OL,9,Fdecided to appoint Mandelson despite
OL,10,Fhim failing the vetting process.
OL,12,FBut a junior minister on Thursday said
OL,13,Fclaims of a Cabinet split over the
OL,14,Fscandal are "a load of guff".
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@\O]
