OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FHome Office minister Alex Norris said:
OL,7,F"If I had a pound, certainly under the
OL,8,Fprevious government, for the number of
OL,9,Ftimes I saw Cabinet stories in the
OL,10,Fpapers, my St George's pints would
OL,11,Fprobably be more multiple than there
OL,12,Fwill be in reality."
OL,14,FResponding to calls from Labour MP
OL,15,FJonathan Brash (Hartlepool) for the
OL,16,Fprime minister to step aside, Mr
OL,17,FNorris insisted that Starmerwould lead
OL,18,FLabour into the next election.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TO]
