OL,3,CRobbins refused to hand over Mandelson
OL,4,Cdocuments, senior civil servant says
OL,6,FThe PM was asked earlier if, at any
OL,7,Fpoint during the Mandelson scandal and
OL,8,Ffallout, he had considered resigning'
OL,10,FStarmer has insisted Robbin's evidence
OL,11,Fabout Mandelson exonerated him over
OL,12,Faccusations that he had misled MPs.
OL,14,FThe mandarin's testimony "puts to bed
OL,15,Fall the allegations levelled at me by
OL,16,Fthose opposite in relation to
OL,17,Fdishonesty", the prime minister said.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUyD@KO]
